        "text": [
          " قَالَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) لَا اعْتِكَافَ إِلَّا بِصَوْمٍ ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.hubeali": [
            "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Muhammad Bin Al Husayn, from Safwan Bin Yahya, from Al A’ala Bin Razeyn, from Muhammad Bin Muslim who said, ",
            "‘Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘There is no <span class=\"iTxt\">Itikaaf</span> except with Fasting’."
          ],
          "en.sarwar": [
            "2. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Muhammad ibn al-Husayn, from Safwan ibn Yahya from al-‘Ala’ ibn Razin from Muhammad ibn Muslim who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Without fast ’I‘tikaf is not valid.’” "
          ]
        }
